<plot>Joseph Martin, a successful French novelist moves to Los Angeles to find the inspiration for his next novel about a sexy Latin tango dancer. Providence will surprise him when one day in the street he finds in Yola - a Mexican immigrant - the new heroin of his book. The couple's personal life gets intertwined with the writer's creative process resulting in a series of unsettling events, which will lead to the inevitable.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?067166</url></doc>
